Package: gcount
Title: Obtain Raw Read Counts from RNASeq Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Arunkumar", "Srinivasan", , "asrinivasan@openanalytics.eu", 
    c("aut", "cre")), person("Open Analytics", role = "cph"))
Maintainer: Arunkumar Srinivasan <asrinivasan@openanalytics.eu>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3)
Imports:
    utils,
    methods,
    gread,
    data.table (>= 1.9.6),
    BiocGenerics,
    S4Vectors,
    GenomicRanges,
    GenomicAlignments,
    bitops
Suggests:
    roxygen2,
    knitr
Description: Count reads that fall under a feature (gene, exon or intron) by
    removing ambiguous and/or overlapping reads for downstream analyses.
